metadata.name: world-beater
metadata.description:
An hour and a half later, the car drove to the southern outskirts of Songguta city and arrived at an old campus - Songguta City Third Vocational High School.



"Put your luggage in the car, take your monster soldiers and pets, and gather on the playground." Gong Cheng stopped the car, looked up in the rearview mirror and shouted, "Can't you understand me?"



The cadets got up and queued hurriedly to get off.



Li Mengnan face floating wind witch doll, arms holding a small color fox, with Du Yu behind the whisper: "this teacher is very fierce oh."
